text: Giving a 4 star instead of 5 because of 2 reasons. 1. Most expensive pizza compared to other places especially with a recent price increase (I have been having jets since 2013 this price increase is very recent if I'm not mistaken) 2. Lack …More

text: I received an email last year for a lunch special. The special clearly stated from 11a-3p, M-F, lunch and pick up only. The manager would not honor my email for the pizza I ordered. He stated that it was old and it will not be honored. The …More

name: Dave Wilburn
text: The most wonderful pizza I have had in a very long time. I got the deep dish with bold pepperoni, Italian sausage and ham. Very tasty, very flavorful. A wonderful taste in the crust. I can't wait to get my next order.

text: I ordered 4 items for delivery, a couple of weeks ago (Feb. 7, 2018). When the driver showed up, 45 minutes after the order was placed, he had only 2 of the four items. He felt badly, and said he's return right away with the other item (I …More

name: Kathy Gerhard
text: We order pizza from Jet's often and each time it taste wonderful and we have never been disappointed.  Service has been great as well.  Thank you Jets!  We will continue to come back.

name: Dave Dunbar
text: Oh yum.  Deep dish is superb.  Excellent quality.  Significantly better than other chains.

name: Lester H.
text: Great deep-dish pizza! Bold pepperoni and turbo crust are excellent!

name: Sanders Family Homestead
text: I ordered a deep dish duo, salad, philly steak and cheese sandwich, and boneless chicken wings. Not only was the guy great over the phone to check for coupons and give us a deal, the food was also excellent!! I never make a comment or post …More

name: Khristian A
text: This is my absolute favorite place to order pizza from. When I get a chance were a friend has not tried this pizza on the weekend when ordering, I HIGHLY recommend ordering from Jet's Pizza. The pizza is very hot when you get it, and the …More

text: If you want your pizza in a timely manner or at all in my case then this is not the place for you

name: lisa charles
text: Not a huge fan of sweet pizza sauce, prefer savory. The bread and toppings were of excellent quality.

name: Clayton Munoz
text: Disappointing customer service. When you pre-tip 20% , the least you expect is parmesan cheese and red pepper. Manager made me feel like it was my fault that the driver wasn't prepared. Sauce was good but the rest of the pizza was average. For the price stick with Pizza hut or Domino's. They always bring cheese and red pepper.

name: Hey Stylo
text: Order the deep dish pizza. Your won’t regret it.

name: James Baron
text: First time to try Jets and had a great experience yesterday. The food was good and the staff member at the counter was a very wonderful and pleasant experience. Highly recommend this location and would recommend their deep dish pizza, salads as well as the sandwiches.

name: Christopher Gregg
text: Love the BBQ chicken. Basically the best alternative deep dish type pizza.

name: sara anderson
text: Ordered from Jet's before and have been happy. Pretty disappointed this time! We ordered a 2X pepperoni, 2x cheese, black olive, and bacon. Double cheese yes. No extra pepperoni and barely any bacon & black olive. If I paid for it, it better be on there :/

name: Mike Murad
text: Slow, expensive and cold. Not a very good pizza. The mgr told me that he would give me a free pizza on my next order.  Not worth a free pizza

name: Zi-on Cheung
text: Yus. Square pan pizza is GENIUS. Every single slice is crispy on all four sides. Got the crunch of a thin crust pizza AND the substance of a deep dish. I hope they make it! I love these guys!

name: A O
text: Love their pizza. If you haven't had it, you need too.

name: Cheryl
text: I used to like this location alright,  but my last two experiences haven't been great.  Most recently I ordered a pizza for delivery,  and 1 hour and 50 minutes later it arrived,  completely cold.  They first attempted to deliver it and the …More

name: Quinten Hope
text: Have always loved this pizza... however, tonight we ordered a single pizza around 6:30’ish. It shows up around 7:00’ish. The driver appears to be a little wasted or just not a very caring person. Hands us the pizza SIDEWAYS and walks off... …More

name: Lynn Martin
text: Great pizza, fast delivery & exceptional customer service!  LOVE the 8 corner deep dish!  I order a couple times a week; delivery guys greet me like a good friend.  If only they had something chocolate for dessert; a brownie would be perfect.  Hhmmm, can't wait for lunch now .....

name: curren burton

text: I ordered it at 6:30 notified me it would be done at 7:00, I sat there for 25 minutes longer that I should have in the loby and then took an extra 20 minutes just to drive home before eating. Pizza was good though.

name: Jerry C
text: The flavor blast the always comes from the first bite is amazing. You can flavorize your crust for free. The price can be a little steep if you aren't getting a special deal. --4.5 stars
